Ruby/RSVG
==============

Ruby/RSVG is a Ruby binding of librsvg2. 

Requirements
------------

    Ruby:               http://www.ruby-lang.org/
    librsvg2:           http://www.gnome.org/

Install
-------

    0. install ruby and librsvg2. 
    1. ruby extconf.rb
    2. make
    3. su
    4. make install

